{"tid":2085630,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方：祖記續約保方基亞連尼一年","createTime":"2020-06-30T03:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:36:23.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4418597211d78e8a614b835f0cf7ffa863228c5b","tid":2085630,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯與傳奇門神保方（Gianluigi Buffon）以及後衛基亞連尼（Giorgio Chiellini）續約一年。<br />\n<br />\n  祖雲達斯的聲明稱：「保方展示出，年齡只是個人的事情&hellip;&hellip;基亞連尼代表著戰鬥和勝利的精神、渴望與決心。」<br />\n<br />\n  保方已經追平了保羅-馬甸尼（Paolo Maldini）647場意甲出場的紀錄，今季正在朝向個人第10個意甲冠軍努力。自從2001年加盟祖雲達斯以後，保方意甲出場479次也保持著球會紀錄。去年夏天從巴黎聖日耳門回歸祖記後，保方成為了施捷斯尼（Wojciech Szczesny）之後的後備門將。<br />\n<br />\n  保方到明年1月將滿43歲，而基亞連尼到8月份就將36歲，兩人都將繼續留在斑馬軍團書寫傳奇。"},{"pid":"c5f023694472bd9cfa0d5c5ed13859b5c2259179","tid":2085630,"uid":235316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e654b7dbac6617b7dd7e337cd29cc6f75c9275b9","tid":2085630,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"repl